WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.867
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.867 --> 00:00:02.983
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.983 --> 00:00:04.834
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:04.834 --> 00:00:11.933
Well, I have my sweetheart with me here again, and I told her, I said, "Man, yesterday's video was powerful.

00:00:11.933 --> 00:00:21.303
If you did not watch that prayer part when the Lord showed up in our prayer time, my goodness, that was life-changing.

00:00:21.303 --> 00:00:27.600
" I told Diana, I said, "I didn't want to stop praying, but I knew that it was—I could feel it lifting.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:30.982
" And so I was like, you know, you only go as long as the Spirit of the Lord is there.

00:00:30.982 --> 00:00:34.580
You're not there to keep doing something if He's not in it.

00:00:34.580 --> 00:00:39.360
But I'm going to do everything with Him, and I'm going to pick it like a chicken bone.

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:56.119
Every time we do those prayer sessions, Diana, the day after or until we make the next video, will go through it looking for scripture references to the things the Father was saying, because we know everything the Lord is going to tell you lines up with His Word.

00:00:56.119 --> 00:01:00.380
He doesn't ever deviate from His Word about revival or anything.

00:01:00.380 --> 00:01:02.959
It always lines up with the Bible.

00:01:02.959 --> 00:01:07.648
And if it doesn't, you really need to realize that 99.

00:01:07.648 --> 00:01:09.952
9% of the time, it's not God.

00:01:09.952 --> 00:01:13.440
If it lines up with scripture, you know it's the Father.

00:01:13.440 --> 00:01:16.720
He's speaking to you because He'll speak, and His Word stands alone.

00:01:16.720 --> 00:01:22.347
It's a pillar, but He always verifies, and the Word lines up with the prophetic.

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:33.893
So, this is the scripture that the Lord was speaking to us about Living Word Church yesterday, and some in Collinsville and Branson.

00:01:34.427 --> 00:01:42.079
He gave us this scripture, and I'm going to have Diana read it here: Psalm 126.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:44.000
Go ahead and read that.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:48.300
"When the Lord brought back his exiles to Jerusalem, it was like a dream.

00:01:48.300 --> 00:01:51.326
We were filled with laughter and we sang for joy.

00:01:51.326 --> 00:01:56.479
And the other nations said, 'What amazing things the Lord has done for them.

00:01:56.479 --> 00:02:00.640
' Yes, the Lord has done amazing things for us.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:01.759
What joy!

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:06.388
Restore our fortunes, Lord, as streams renew the desert.

00:02:06.388 --> 00:02:11.120
Those who plant in tears will harvest with shouts of joy.

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:17.360
They weep as they go to plant their seed, but they sing as they return with the harvest.

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:20.390
" So He was quoting to us verse five.

00:02:20.390 --> 00:02:22.400
Go ahead and read verse 5.

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:26.356
"Those who plant in tears will harvest with shouts of joy.

00:02:26.356 --> 00:02:33.440
They weep as they go to plant their seed, but they sing as they return with the harvest.

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:36.879
" He's talking about the harvest that's about to take place.

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:37.360
Exciting.

00:02:38.709 --> 00:02:43.160
So, let's just get right into the vision, what He showed us yesterday.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:51.840
Like I said, I am not really familiar with Living Word, but He keeps talking about Minnesota and what's going to happen in Minnesota.

00:02:51.840 --> 00:03:00.239
And then what was awesome is—and we'll get into this—He talked about what's about to happen in California and all these other areas.

00:03:01.062 --> 00:03:05.519
I'm telling you, this vision that we had yesterday was wow.

00:03:05.519 --> 00:03:09.440
So, I encourage you to watch this whole video because it will really bless you.

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:15.180
If you didn't watch the whole prayer video yesterday, I encourage you to go back and watch it again.

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:22.000
Listen to the prayer part, what was coming right out of the throne room of the Father.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:30.293
Now, I was seeing Lynne Hammond, who is the pastor over Living Word with her husband Mac.

00:03:30.293 --> 00:03:35.120
And so, she is the prayer warrior.

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:38.220
She's the one that prays like what I'm talking about.

00:03:38.220 --> 00:03:42.249
But I saw her as a younger woman in this vision.

00:03:42.249 --> 00:03:47.600
I saw her as a younger woman when they first started the church, and I saw her praying alone.

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:50.980
She was praying and travailing for the lost.

00:03:50.980 --> 00:03:54.720
And as she would pray, people would be added.

00:03:54.983 --> 00:04:00.994
I saw these people that were strategically placed at Living Word for prayer.

00:04:01.428 --> 00:04:15.142
They would rise up beside her, and as she prayed, it was like a fire torch inside of her that would catch on to that other person, and then they would catch the fire and start praying.

00:04:15.519 --> 00:04:23.223
As the prayers of that church group, or whoever was praying there, each one would pray, and the fire would spread.

00:04:25.336 --> 00:04:28.560
I could see the prayer group getting bigger and bigger and bigger.

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:34.520
But as they were praying, they were sowing seeds into the ground.

00:04:34.970 --> 00:04:42.389
I could see in that vision thick, manure-looking soil that was rich, like Miracle-Gro soil.

00:04:45.320 --> 00:04:51.303
But the seeds went—not growing, but they went dormant.

00:04:51.303 --> 00:05:01.257
They went into the ground and were being held, not for then, but they were praying for what's about to happen.

00:05:03.100 --> 00:05:09.160
Some of the time they thought, "Well, Lord," crying out and weeping, and that's the scripture He gave us.

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:12.960
They were sowing in their tears, but they're about to reap in joy.

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:29.539
They were sowing these tears of prayers, and they were going into the foundation of the church, and they never saw the full manifestation of all the years of prayers, from Brother Halverson to Lucy when she was here on the earth.

00:05:29.539 --> 00:05:38.180
There were so many prayers of the saints that went into the ground, and you'd see a couple sprouts of growth here and there.

00:05:38.180 --> 00:05:47.760
And there was a beginning revival that was a former—what you want to call a former rain of that church, a former glory.

00:05:47.760 --> 00:05:54.720
And the Lord said to me, I saw those seeds as they prayed in these prayer groups.

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:55.893
I saw a heavy-set woman.

00:05:55.893 --> 00:05:57.066
I don't know who she was.

00:05:57.066 --> 00:06:00.800
I saw all these people, and they were in circles, and they just kept at it.

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:01.760
They kept planting.

00:06:01.760 --> 00:06:02.080
They kept planting.

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:09.051
And the Lord said, "Some plant, some water, and some bring forth the increase.

00:06:09.051 --> 00:06:20.460
" Not every one of the seeds in the past from the elders, from Rachel Tateller to all these great prayer warriors—Jeannie Wilkerson, all these great prayer warriors that I've mentioned before.

00:06:20.460 --> 00:06:27.199
He said they didn't see the full manifestation of what they sowed in prayer.

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:30.826
But the next generation grabbed on a little bit more, and it went on.

00:06:30.826 --> 00:06:32.039
But it went clear back.

00:06:32.289 --> 00:06:55.900
It went back even further decades, another generation, generations of people that have wept and wept and wept for the coming of the Lord, for the coming of the Messiah, waiting for the former rain and the latter rain, sowing seeds of tears of prayers for the foundation of the revival that's about to take place.

00:06:55.900 --> 00:07:05.680
They were sowing it in the ground, and I could see before the Father's throne these beautiful seeds that were planted, but you couldn't see them.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:13.770
They were in the dirt, and they were dormant, and the Lord said these dormant seeds have all been planted.

00:07:13.770 --> 00:07:29.097
And as I was watching in this church of Living Word in Minnesota, all of a sudden those seeds got water on them that was coming from the throne, and it started to saturate.

00:07:29.097 --> 00:07:34.200
You could hear me talking about it in the vision, and it was a thick water that was glorious.

00:07:34.200 --> 00:07:40.159
I saw glory like water coming, but it covered the seeds with this manure, right?

00:07:40.159 --> 00:07:42.684
And I saw the water come on top of it.

00:07:42.684 --> 00:07:51.866
So all of a sudden I saw corn stalks start coming up in the middle of the altars, of all the pews where the chairs were.

00:07:51.866 --> 00:07:57.360
They started springing forth, and it started springing forth corn plants all over the place.

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.880
There were corn plants.

00:07:58.880 --> 00:08:08.480
But as those seeds were being watered—some plant, some water, and some bring forth the increase.

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:18.960
The Lord said to me, He said, "You're about to see the generation that's about to bring in the increase, the harvest time.

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:26.596
" And I saw Living Word, I saw Lynne as, like I said, a young woman, and she kept praying.

00:08:26.596 --> 00:08:37.960
And then all of a sudden I saw a glory mist fill the congregation, and as it was coming onto the congregation members—this is what's about to happen.

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:40.280
And the Lord showed me what's about to happen.

00:08:40.280 --> 00:08:41.720
I saw Holy Ghost mist.

00:08:41.720 --> 00:08:43.316
It looked like a fog.

00:08:43.316 --> 00:08:55.342
But as it went onto the people, as it lifted and went away, it left a residue of gold dust.

00:08:56.480 --> 00:09:01.831
It was like gold dust all over the people.

00:09:01.831 --> 00:09:11.360
As this mist lifted, it left gold dust and diamond-like particles of diamonds, but they shone like a sparkling on their clothes.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.240
Wow.

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:30.231
And the Lord told me, He said, 'There have been times in the past in other church services, not with Living Word but with other churches, that people have tried to mimic and try to imitate what God has done and what has been pure in times past.

00:09:30.231 --> 00:09:40.168
But this will be a new movement of a fragrance, of a beautiful outpouring of the Spirit of God like we've never seen it before.

00:09:40.168 --> 00:09:46.480
As the mist comes in, as it lifts, it will leave gold dust on folks.

00:09:46.900 --> 00:09:49.466
I'll be excited just with the mist.

00:09:49.466 --> 00:09:51.590
I mean, I'm rolling around in that mist cloud.

00:09:51.590 --> 00:09:53.700
If I'm seeing the mist, I'm like, this is...

00:09:54.450 --> 00:09:57.839
But God's doing another little bit of something to this.

00:09:57.839 --> 00:10:08.320
Not only is it—it's not like when you get mist in real life and it leaves a residue of moisture on your skin, some humidity, or when you walk in fog you feel humidity like the dew.

00:10:09.306 --> 00:10:18.810
But the Lord said as this happens in services, it will leave a gold dust, almost like when you see dust on your furniture, a residue of the glory.

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:23.572
Wow.

00:10:23.572 --> 00:10:29.547
And I could see—this is what I thought was interesting—I saw where they are right now.

00:10:29.547 --> 00:10:45.440
And this is me, I'm not picking at the church, I don't know these people, but I saw from COVID to where they are now that the numbers are down, that things aren't like they were in the past with people showing up for prayer.

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:48.675
Now, I don't know if this is true or not, but this is just what I saw.

00:10:48.675 --> 00:10:51.640
Now, if you go there and you say, "Brandon, that's off.

00:10:51.640 --> 00:10:53.324
" Well, then call me off, but whatever.

00:10:53.555 --> 00:10:56.099
This is what I saw, and I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:10:56.099 --> 00:11:00.000
I don't add anything to or take away from anything that I see.

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:11.120
But I saw a wave that was back in the '80s and '90s, that was strong prayer that came in like a wave.

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:24.240
And as the years have gone by, the wave has receded, and there's dryness in between.

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:27.143
Where the beach is, there's dryness there.

00:11:27.143 --> 00:11:33.467
And as the water keeps pulling back, the drier it gets on the beach.

00:11:33.467 --> 00:11:40.000
But the Lord said to me, 'What seems dry right now is not dryness.

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:47.230
It's getting ready for another major wave of My glory and prayer on that church and on these other churches around the nation.

00:11:47.230 --> 00:12:01.200
' And I saw a tsunami wave, because the further the water is being pulled back, just like it is in a tsunami—it's pulling it back, pulling it back—all of a sudden, you go, 'Where's the water?

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:05.560
' and it's 500 feet way back that way.

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:09.866
People go, 'What happened to the water?

00:12:09.866 --> 00:12:10.629
The water's receding.

00:12:10.629 --> 00:12:12.171
Man, this is really bad.

00:12:12.171 --> 00:12:19.387
' And then all of a sudden you go, 'No, you need to run because there's about to be a major tidal wave of God's presence and glory.

00:12:19.387 --> 00:12:21.640
' And that is what's happening right now.

00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:31.245
The Lord said, 'You may say it's dry right now in the natural in the body of Christ, and what you feel right now in the natural, and not just concerning Living Word.

00:12:31.245 --> 00:12:41.349
' But He said, 'What you're seeing in the body of Christ right now seems really dry, Brandon, but what's happening is that wave is being pulled back.

00:12:41.691 --> 00:12:53.999
Get ready, because a major tsunami of My glory and My presence is about to invade America, it's about to invade South America, and it's about to invade all around the world.

00:12:53.999 --> 00:12:59.680
All around this world is about to have a major tsunami wave of the glory of God.

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:04.160
' Because where it is the driest, it's because the water's receding.

00:13:04.400 --> 00:13:13.680
Get ready, because the Lord told me, He said, 'A major wave of My presence is about to invade this earth one more time, one more time.

00:13:13.680 --> 00:13:20.109
' And that's what I saw, the glory pulling back, and it was beautiful.

00:13:20.109 --> 00:13:22.274
So she's going to cry again.

00:13:28.790 --> 00:13:29.146
I sure love you; your heart is so tender.

00:13:29.146 --> 00:13:34.143
So as I saw that happening, then I saw that coming, and then it was like this.

00:13:34.768 --> 00:13:41.760
I saw it was like a rock that is being thrown in the middle of a pond.

00:13:42.370 --> 00:13:49.230
It doesn't just ripple one way; it creates a tidal wave all around it.

00:13:49.230 --> 00:14:02.720
And as Lynn was praying, I saw what's about to take place with the new generation, where the elderly generation is tired and they've done their part.

00:14:02.720 --> 00:14:12.840
And I saw runners running, and they were running in a sprint, but they didn't stop in stride to turn back and look and grab.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:22.756
They were running in stride and they caught on to what the elders had, and they grabbed a hold of the baton of the glory and they ran with it even further because they had young legs.

00:14:22.756 --> 00:14:32.860
But as this happened, I saw a rock in the middle of a pool of water, and the wave of the glory didn't just hit one way.

00:14:32.860 --> 00:14:34.659
It exploded all the way around.

00:14:34.659 --> 00:14:40.359
It had ripples to the north, the south, the east, the west, the northwest—all the way around, it was a ripple all around.

00:14:41.920 --> 00:14:54.175
But then I saw this: I saw old buses that looked like school buses going out from Living Word, and they were packing these buses full of people and they were evangelizing.

00:14:54.511 --> 00:14:57.540
People were getting healed with creative miracles and things were happening.

00:14:57.750 --> 00:15:02.128
I don't know if they do this or not, but I'm telling you this is what I saw.

00:15:02.520 --> 00:15:08.340
I saw new, fresh faces, a new, fresh revival coming to this church.

00:15:08.340 --> 00:15:12.777
And the Lord was warning me, He said, 'Brandon, I'm not done.

00:15:12.777 --> 00:15:14.914
' You may think the water's coming back.

00:15:14.914 --> 00:15:15.710
They may think...

00:15:15.710 --> 00:15:18.765
I don't know, this church could be totally on fire.

00:15:18.765 --> 00:15:20.126
You might say, 'Brandon, this is totally off.

00:15:20.126 --> 00:15:23.610
' I don't know; all I know is this is what the Lord is showing me.

00:15:23.610 --> 00:15:29.546
Maybe there's still a little fire there, or from where it was, I don't know.

00:15:29.813 --> 00:15:31.680
I'm just telling you what I see.

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:39.040
But then the Lord showed me, I saw Azusa Street in California.

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:48.079
And He told me, 'This church, Living Word, will become a new Azusa Street revival.

00:15:48.079 --> 00:16:01.166
' And He said, 'Not only will Living Word become Azusa Street, but Collinsville, Branson, California again, all these other churches.

00:16:01.166 --> 00:16:10.116
' And He said to me, 'There will be multiple Azusa Street revival strong points in Fort Worth.

00:16:10.116 --> 00:16:11.474
I saw Eagle Mountain.

00:16:11.474 --> 00:16:24.420
I saw these places for strong points of revival that are about to hit the land, and it will be like pillars of fire in the spirit realm, like what they saw in Azusa Street, that people will be coming there.

00:16:24.420 --> 00:16:29.853
' Oh, and then He showed me Charis Bible College for Andrew Wommack.

00:16:29.853 --> 00:16:33.872
Andrew Wommack was another place of like an Azusa Street revival in Colorado Springs, Colorado.

00:16:34.760 --> 00:16:40.651
I saw a major revival about to take place at Charis Bible College.

00:16:40.651 --> 00:16:44.939
And the Lord said to me, He said, 'It's all hands on deck right now.

00:16:44.939 --> 00:16:46.880
I'm calling all the generals.

00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:50.496
I'm calling whoever will just say yes to Me.

00:16:50.496 --> 00:16:53.314
I will pour out My Spirit upon all flesh.

00:16:53.314 --> 00:16:59.600
' And that's why He told me, He said, 'Brandon, you've been criticized about the visions that I give you.

00:16:59.600 --> 00:17:05.899
And people say, "Well, he sees more visions and more things than even the prophets of old saw.

00:17:05.899 --> 00:17:10.536
" But the Lord said, "Brandon, all you're doing is fulfilling Joel chapter 2.

00:17:10.536 --> 00:17:18.880
In the last days, I said, I'll pour out My Spirit upon all flesh, and my young men will see visions, and my old men will dream dreams.

00:17:18.880 --> 00:17:21.973
"' And He said, 'Brandon, you're fulfilling that word.

00:17:21.973 --> 00:17:24.586
Don't worry about what they say.

00:17:24.586 --> 00:17:25.951
You're fulfilling that word.

00:17:25.951 --> 00:17:28.440
' He said it to me again and He keeps telling me.

00:17:28.440 --> 00:17:29.177
He said, 'Don't worry.

00:17:29.771 --> 00:17:32.799
Young men will see visions and old men will dream dreams.

00:17:32.799 --> 00:17:34.766
' The old men are going to start to dream lots of dreams.

00:17:34.766 --> 00:17:36.759
They're going to tell you about what they're seeing.

00:17:36.759 --> 00:17:40.480
People are going to have visitations about hell.

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:49.040
The Lord said, 'I'm going to show them and give them warnings to come back and give them a place and a platform to tell what they saw in hell.

00:17:49.040 --> 00:17:51.560
' If you have people reach out about that, that's what He told me.

00:17:51.560 --> 00:17:52.994
He said they're going to reach out.

00:17:52.994 --> 00:17:58.180
People are going to start talking about hell, and we'll know the authentic from the fake.

00:17:58.180 --> 00:18:02.400
You're going to know what God is saying—this is from Me and who's not.

00:18:02.951 --> 00:18:13.520
And I'm telling you all by the Spirit of God, people are going to start having visitations and manifestations of the glory of angelic hosts like we've never seen before.

00:18:13.520 --> 00:18:14.891
It's time to believe.

00:18:14.891 --> 00:18:16.466
It's time to receive.

00:18:16.466 --> 00:18:23.200
It's time to expect everything God has for you in these last days.

00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:30.559
Sister Billye called right after I uploaded that video and she goes, "Okay, tell me the scoop.

00:18:30.559 --> 00:18:32.352
What did you see?

00:18:32.352 --> 00:18:33.340
I want to know.

00:18:33.340 --> 00:18:35.634
" And I said, "I didn't send that video to you.

00:18:35.634 --> 00:18:36.389
Somebody else did.

00:18:36.389 --> 00:18:37.867
So, somebody watches my channel.

00:18:37.867 --> 00:18:40.368
" So, I'm thankful for whoever's out there supporting me.

00:18:40.368 --> 00:18:45.769
I just want to let you all know Jesus is the reason for this.

00:18:45.769 --> 00:19:04.194
And I'm so excited to be a part, you know, as we see what he's about to do in Living Word, and the prayers of the saints that were buried in the sand that people thought had gone dormant and they never saw the full manifestation of what they're believing for there.

00:19:04.194 --> 00:19:08.880
Those seeds are about to spring forth fruit all around the world.

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:14.274
And I saw the glorious gospel in a way that we've never seen before.

00:19:14.274 --> 00:19:30.766
And then I saw a major revival about to hit California, and I told you all that, and he even said, "Remember the Welsh revival where they had to train the donkeys to go on different commands other than by swear words?

00:19:30.766 --> 00:19:46.960
" Because there was so much revival that took place in Welsh that people were so foul and had bad language that the donkeys didn't know how to operate in the commands they were being told because they were just used to being sweared at all the time.

00:19:46.960 --> 00:19:51.749
And the miners all got born again, and it was like Sunday there all the time.

00:19:51.749 --> 00:20:05.520
There was a glorious outpouring that happened in the Welsh revival, and the Lord showed me, he said, "The porn industry will dry up for a season because of what's going to happen in Hollywood.

00:20:05.520 --> 00:20:13.320
" He said, "Brandon, I'm going to visit Hollywood, for the deeper the blue, the greater the revival.

00:20:13.320 --> 00:20:16.720
" And remember, "I'm going to show up in Hollywood.

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:29.600
" And I saw certain key celebrities, major A-list celebrities, giving their heart to Jesus Christ and having indoor meetings in mansions.

00:20:29.600 --> 00:20:36.206
But as this happens, there will be people so hungry in these glory domes.

00:20:36.206 --> 00:20:45.733
Instead of sports domes, there'll be glory events, and there will be so much of this going on that people won't be looking at bad stuff on the internet for a little bit.

00:20:45.733 --> 00:20:49.930
They'll be so tied up and so excited about repentance that they'll be like, "Man!

00:20:49.930 --> 00:20:52.720
